data.title: Poetry Toolkit
data.content: Tools for inspiring poets! Built with Python, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, PostgreSQL, React, Flask, Jinja2, SQLAlchemy, Bootstrap, and using the PoetryDB API.

data.title: BirdDex
data.content: A very familiar looking encyclopedia of (mostly nonfictional) birds. A collaboration with the fabulous @bethanylynn (check out her Github)!

data.title: Silverstone Contracting
data.content: A playful and colorful website for a small business in California. Python/Flask, HTML, CSS. Mobile-first design. Built and designed in collaboration with the wonderful @dr-acc (check out her GitHub)!

data.title: Empower Counseling
data.content: (Still under construction!) A clean and inviting design for a private practice in Tennessee. Python/Flask, HTML, CSS. Mobile-first design. Built and designed with the talented @alexray113 (Check out their GitHub)!

data.title: CSV Converter
data.content: A simple Python project to easily convert a CSV file into a JSON file. Front-end integration coming soon!
